'''2021年吉布提總統選舉'''於2021年4月9日（星期五）舉行。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/djibouti-election/djibouti-president-seen-winning-fifth-term-in-election-idUSL8N2M11LJ |title=Djibouti president seen winning fifth term in election |publisher=Reuters |date=2021-04-09 |accessdate=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410180547/https://www.reuters.com/article/djibouti-election/djibouti-president-seen-winning-fifth-term-in-election-idUSL8N2M11LJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1999年上台的時任總統[[伊斯梅尔·奥马尔·盖莱|伊斯梅尔·奥马尔·盖莱]]在首輪投票以超過97%的得票率成功連任。主要反對派杯葛了本次選舉。<ref name=france24>{{Cite news |url=https://www.france24.com/en/africa/20210410-djibouti-s-veteran-ruler-guelleh-re-elected-for-fifth-term |title=Djibouti's veteran ruler Guelleh re-elected for fifth term |website=France 24 |date=2021-04-10 |accessdate=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517121057/https://www.france24.com/en/africa/20210410-djibouti-s-veteran-ruler-guelleh-re-elected-for-fifth-term |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==選舉制度==
總統選舉採取[[兩輪投票制|兩輪投票制]]。如果首輪投票有候選人取得過半數票即勝選，無需舉行次輪投票。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|journal=Journel officiel de la République de Djibouti|title=Loi Constitutionnelle n°92/AN/10/6ème L portant révision de la Constitution|url=http://www.rodra.co.za/images/countries/djibouti/legislation/portant%20révision%20de%20la%20Constitution%2092%202010.pdf|access-date=2021-04-09|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209175232/http://www.rodra.co.za/images/countries/djibouti/legislation/portant%20r%C3%A9vision%20de%20la%20Constitution%2092%202010.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

